"How YouTube Counts Views, Fights View Bots, and Tracks You More Than You Think"


monitoring video rendering + user interaction

cookies helo YT identify unique users and track their browsing behaviour

youtube defines quality views that are views which meet certain criteria like
duration - 30 seconds
engagement - user must interact with the video : click, scroll, hover over the video player
glitches - the video must be played without any glitches errors or technical issues


youtube filters out repeated plays from the same IP / Device in a short time to avoid manipulation

Youtube also filters suspicious views after backend processing  